# ===== OpenAI Configuration =====
# Option 1: Direct OpenAI API (RECOMMENDED)
# Get your key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-api-key-here

# Option 2: Azure OpenAI (comment out OPENAI_API_KEY to use Azure)
# IMPORTANT: Use GA Protocol URL format (not Beta Protocol)
# Get these from your Azure OpenAI resource
AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://your-resource.openai.azure.com
AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT=gpt-realtime-mini
AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=your-azure-api-key-here
# Note: AZURE_OPENAI_API_VERSION is no longer needed for GA Protocol
